description: Mineral Mountain Resources Ltd., an exploration stage company, acquires, explores for, and develops mineral properties in North America. Its flagship project is the Standby gold project covering an area of 67.45 acres located in Black Hills of South Dakota, the United States. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. R. Dale Ginn B.Sc., P.Geo., P.Geol.
